# directio64.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 

### Description

directio64.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: afed9dff-245e-4875-a156-3c5584beed03
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create directio64.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\directio64.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start directio64.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
